title: Seijo ni Naru node Nidome no Jinsei wa Katteni Sasete Moraimasu: Outaishi wa, Zense de Watashi wo Futta Koibito Deshita
altTitle: Since I Became a Saint, I'll Do Whatever I Want with My Second Life: The Prince Was My Lover Who Threw Me Away in My Previous Life
聖女になるので二度目の人生は勝手にさせてもらいます ～王太子は、前世で私を振った恋人でした～
